Any sort of block, denoted by a block name and curly braces, like so:
    The parsed block:
        block name {
            content 1;
            content 2;
        }
    might be represented with the list [names, contents], where
        names = ["block", " ", "name", " "]
        contents = [["
    ", "content", " ", "1"], ["
    ", "content", " ", "2"], "
"]
